public class ListFormatter
extends Formatter

ListFormatter is a subclass of Formatter which is responsible for formatting, parsing, and comparing vectors.

getValue

public Object getValue(Object object,
                       Locale locale)
Returns a List from the given object. We currently do not support converting other object types to List, so the method will either return the List that is passed in or, if the object isn't a List, it will return null.

Specified by:
getValue in class Formatter
Parameters:
object - the object to convert to a List

a List derived from the given object
